sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Buyer as Buyer Client
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant Router as Express API Router
    participant BookCtrl as Booking Controller
    participant DB as PostgreSQL Database
    participant LedgerSrv as Ledger Service
    participant OwnerFE as Owner Frontend UI
    actor Owner as Equipment Owner

    Buyer->>FE: Select Equipment & Booking Dates
    FE->>Router: POST /api/bookings {listingId, startDate, endDate}
    Router->>BookCtrl: createBooking(req, res)
    BookCtrl->>DB: Query listing details (ownerId, price, status)
    DB-->>BookCtrl: Listing Info
    BookCtrl->>BookCtrl: Compute duration & total cost
    BookCtrl->>DB: INSERT INTO bookings status='pending'
    DB-->>BookCtrl: Booking Record
    BookCtrl->>DB: Create booking notification for Owner
    BookCtrl-->>FE: 201 Booking Created (Pending Confirmation)
    FE-->>Buyer: Show "Awaiting Owner Confirmation"

    Note over Owner, BookCtrl: Owner Acceptance Phase
    Owner->>OwnerFE: Click "Accept Booking Request"
    OwnerFE->>Router: POST /api/bookings/:id/confirm
    Router->>BookCtrl: confirmBooking(req, res)
    BookCtrl->>DB: UPDATE bookings SET status = 'confirmed'
    
    rect rgb(255, 240, 245)
        Note over BookCtrl, LedgerSrv: Cryptographic Ledger Chain Assembly
        BookCtrl->>LedgerSrv: writeLedgerEntry(listingId, renterId, ownerId, amount, duration)
        LedgerSrv->>DB: SELECT block_hash FROM rental_ledger ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 1
        DB-->>LedgerSrv: Returns Last Block Hash (or '0' if first)
        LedgerSrv->>LedgerSrv: Generate random txId UUID
        LedgerSrv->>LedgerSrv: hashRecord(txId, listingId, renterId, ownerId, amount, days, prevHash)
        Note over LedgerSrv: block_hash = SHA256(JSON(tx_data) + prevHash)
        LedgerSrv->>LedgerSrv: hashAgreement(txId, listingId, renterId, ownerId, amount, days)
        Note over LedgerSrv: agreement_hash = SHA256(Agreement string)
        LedgerSrv->>DB: INSERT INTO rental_ledger (tx_id, prev_hash, block_hash, agreement_hash, ...)
        DB-->>LedgerSrv: Ledger Block saved
        LedgerSrv-->>BookCtrl: Block entry confirmed
    end
    
    BookCtrl->>DB: Create notification for Buyer
    BookCtrl-->>OwnerFE: 200 Booking Confirmed & Secured
    OwnerFE-->>Owner: Display "Booking Confirmed"
